==Internationalization==
[[The Bat!]] supports [[Email Address Internationalization]] (EAI).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.idnnews.com/?p=10045 |title=Starting with the version 6.0 The Bat! supports IDN (Internationalized Domain Names))}}</ref>{{better source|date=October 2013}}{{discuss|International email}}

As of October 2016, email clients supporting [[Extended SMTP#SMTPUTF8|SMTPUTF8]] included Outlook 2016,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://support.office.com/en-US/article/International-email-addresses-303595ea-4893-4b26-9b14-2202c32fea36|title=International email addresses - Outlook|website=support.office.com|access-date=2016-10-27}}</ref> mail for iOS, and mail for Android.{{citation needed|date=January 2018}}

